      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been meticulously cared for, always garaged, and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without the dealership price tag, this is the one for you. Come see it for yourself, you seriously won't be disappointed!",
