    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Vanos. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a documented subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary structural concern. The valve lash has been recently shimmed to factory specifications, and the variable M differential lock provides optimal torque distribution. With zero fluid seepage and a pristine undercarriage, this vehicle maintains its original mechanical tolerances and delivers a pure, analog driving experience.",
